task.summary:
Remove firebase auth
only use Unity Authentication

250416
Google Login Success.
Apple Login must be tested.

250425
User Account Delete Method Added. - Hard delete - With cascade delete enabled, all keys associated with the user are automatically deleted when the user is removed.
A new property has been added to the User table. - The 'Login Method' property has been added. - It specifies how the user logged in (e.g., Apple, Google).

Summary 250427
DB version upgraded to 0.2v - User table has been divided into User and User Auth. - Friend table has only one row. - Daily product table will be added.

250429
New table added. - Daily Product set. - Logic for Displaying Daily Product will be added.
UserSubscription Table Added. - Managing user's subscriptions such as GoldenPass, Ads Remover. - All payment history can be managed by UserSubscriptionHistory table.

feat(Database - AbbDbContext): DataModel changed.
- Rename Column [Probability -> Weight] on DailyProduct Table. - Add Column 'Class' on DailyProduct Table to distinct card colour by class for client.

feat(Database-AppDbContext)
DailyProduct Table has been divided into 'DailyProduct' and 'DailyFreeProduct'.

feat(DB-AppDbContext) Add Column
Add Column [NeedAds] to UserDailyProduct Table to distinguish the products to need to watch ads.
[InitProductPacketResponse] has DailyProductInfo, client can display daily products for each user.

feat(API) Product Init Method
Daily product will be initiated when client logs in.

feat(DB) New Column
NeedAds column has been added into table UserDailyProduct

feat(PaymentController) Get DailyProducts
Error for creating daily product set has been fixed.

feat(Controller) Web Packet Modified
Class 'UserInfo' in Web Packet has a new property 'UserAccount' from UserAuth DB to bind user account into user manager instance on client.

feat(Web) Terms and Privacy
Terms and Privacy has been created. It will be shown by users who want to read Terms and Privacy after logging in. It will be shown by browser, hamonstudio.net.

feat(Database) New Column Added.
Column 'PolicyAgreed' has been added to verify if the user agreed our policies.

feat(Controller) AdsController.cs
Reward for watching rewarded video will be granted.
feat(Service) User Sign up error solved.

feat(DB, Controller) New column added, reward added
'Price' column has been added to table 'DailyProduct'. The price of daily product should be cheaper than original price.
Api logic for reward after watching rewarded video has been created.

feat(DB, Controller) Applying ads remover
New column added - Column 'Price' to table 'DailyProduct'
Some methods - Methods related ads remover are added. - Refreshing daily products - Timer for refreshing button has been created.

feat(DB) User Tutorial Table Changed.
PK has been changed to 'UserTutorialId'. One of exist Key 'TutorialType' is mutable if new type of tutorial added.
